%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=PiwLpsDni%2BEQUOLZDbBUzxZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=b09dd93c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a><br />\n官方link (我們香港人計劃) :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2F&d=PiwLpsDni%2BEQUOLZDbBUzxZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=fe890ca9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/</a><br />\n<br />\n(對唔住，咁危難時刻下我知而家仲叫大家課金可能好反感，但我相信兄弟爬山，各有各做，行得通就全力去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"98a26e0cf99b76655bf2e372fe20958bf0ed7b45","tid":1728342,"uid":43061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0819282baef152e794c83b236aebeaa3a35bc4b1","tid":1728342,"uid":46435,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f9b5fdf2e34bd448f02fe37fd781c7b4543e1eb7","tid":1728342,"uid":43061,"like":3,"dislike":42,"score":-39,"quote":{"pid":"1b50cda87c380c19adca5bee1a61f4568d799a22","tid":1728342,"uid":224741,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T23:41:48.000Z","msg":"投hk protest yes, 投no bts<br />\n<a href=\"https://time.com/person-of-the-year-poll-2019/?go=true\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2Fperson-of-the-year-poll-2019%2F%3Fgo%3Dtrue&d=PiwLpsDni%2BEQUOLZDbBUzxZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=3a528081\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://time.com/person-of-the-year-poll-2019/?go=true</a>"},"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T00:10:45.000Z","msg":"投左bts 支持v仔"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T00:43:08.000Z","msg":"疤人好波"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T00:43:38.000Z","msg":"再叫唔客氣"},{"pid":"2aa1da5693844ebdb91cda502b6a63031230547e","tid":1728342,"uid":88491,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"98a26e0cf99b76655bf2e372fe20958bf0ed7b45","tid":1728342,"uid":43061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0819282baef152e794c83b236aebeaa3a35bc4b1","tid":1728342,"uid":46435,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote"